<h2>🏠 New Rental Application Received</h2>

<p>Hello {{ownerName}},</p>

<p>Great news! You have received a new rental application for your property <strong>{{property.title}}</strong>.</p>

<div style="background-color: #f8fafc; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #10b981;">
    <h3>📋 Application Details</h3>
    <p><strong>Property:</strong> {{property.title}}</p>
    <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{property.address}}, {{property.city}}, {{property.state}}</p>
    <p><strong>Monthly Rent:</strong> ₹{{property.monthlyRent}}</p>
</div>

<div style="background-color: #fff7ed; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;">
    <h3>👤 Applicant Information</h3>
    <p><strong>Name:</strong> {{tenant.name}}</p>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{tenant.email}}</p>
    <p><strong>Phone:</strong> {{tenant.phone}}</p>
    <p><strong>Address:</strong> {{tenant.address}}</p>
</div>

{{#if applicationText}}
<div style="background-color: #f0f9ff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;">
    <h3>💬 Applicant's Message</h3>
    <p><em>"{{applicationText}}"</em></p>
</div>
{{/if}}

<h3>⚡ Quick Actions</h3>
<p>You can review and respond to this application:</p>

<div style="margin: 20px 0;">
    <a href="#" class="button-primary" style="background-color: #10b981; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-block; margin-right: 10px;">✅ Approve Application</a>
    <a href="#" class="button-secondary" style="background-color: #6b7280; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-block; margin-right: 10px;">❌ Reject Application</a>
</div>

<a href="#" class="button-secondary" style="background-color: #3b82f6; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-block;">📋 View Full Application</a>

<div class="divider" style="border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 30px 0;"></div>

<h3>💡 Tips for Property Owners</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Respond Promptly:</strong> Quick responses help secure quality tenants</li>
    <li><strong>Screen Carefully:</strong> Review all documents and conduct background checks</li>
    <li><strong>Professional Communication:</strong> Maintain professional correspondence throughout</li>
    <li><strong>Set Clear Expectations:</strong> Clearly communicate lease terms and requirements</li>
</ul>

<h3>📞 Need Help?</h3>
<p>If you need assistance with tenant screening or have questions about the application process:</p>

<a href="#" class="button-secondary" style="background-color: #6b7280; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-block;">Contact Support</a>

<p>Thank you for using RentalEase to manage your properties.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
<strong>The RentalEase Team</strong></p>